        </p>
        <p>
          <a class="naked" href="https://app.netlify.com/start/deploy?repository=https://github.com/netlify/example-site-boilerplate"><img src="https://www.netlify.com/img/deploy/button.svg" alt="Deploy to Netlify"></a>
        </p>
      </section>
      <section>
        Made with <img class="netliheart" title="love" src="/images/netliheart.svg" alt="love" width="1em"> by the <a href="https://netlify.com">Netlify</a> team. Explore <a href="https://github.com/netlify/example-site-boilerplate">the code</a> in GitHub. Follow <a href="https://twitter.com/netlify">@Netliify</a> on Twitter for regular updates</a>.
      </section>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

